Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 15:10:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix(rfork): support quantized and draft transfers

Support RFork transfer for Ascend quantized models by transferring the post-load tensor layout instead of raw checkpoint parameters.

Add MTP draft model worker isolation, RFork seed shape metadata handling, chunked transfer, transfer state cleanup, and layer_sharding fallback to the default loader.

- vLLM version: v0.22.1
- vLLM main: https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/commit/967c5c3bc38891f4465d3f4e99917ed837bb3833

Signed-off-by: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
